title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight -  Helicopter Sikorsky H34 - version 0.4
description:
In this video we will look at the Sikorsky H34 helicopter which has been released today. Although the helicopter is still under development I am really surprised by the stage it is already. After completing a review from the exterior we look at the cockpit and take off for a short flight.

If you also want to give this aircraft a try download your own copy from:
https://flightsim.to/file/25096/native-helicopter-sikorsky-h34
